<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1436,450,537]" pageId="18" pageNumber="25">
Valves elliptic with short apiculate apices. Valve length 
<quantity box="[783,900,450,473]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.3" metricValueMax="7.2" metricValueMin="5.4" pageId="18" pageNumber="25" unit="mm" value="63.0" valueMax="72.0" valueMin="54.0">54–72 µm</quantity>
; valve width 
<quantity box="[1056,1174,450,473]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" metricValueMax="3.9" metricValueMin="3.1" pageId="18" pageNumber="25" unit="mm" value="35.0" valueMax="39.0" valueMin="31.0">31–39 µm</quantity>
. One to 3 (typically 2) undulations evident across the valve face. Marginal ribs regularly spaced, 
<quantity box="[994,1062,482,505]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.159" metricValueMax="2.286" metricValueMin="2.032" pageId="18" pageNumber="25" unit="in" value="8.5" valueMax="9.0" valueMin="8.0">8–9 in</quantity>
<quantity box="[1069,1142,482,505]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="18" pageNumber="25" unit="mm" value="10.0">10 µm</quantity>
. Striae very irregular, often disorganized, 
<quantity box="[348,429,514,537]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.302" metricValueMax="4.572" metricValueMin="2.032" pageId="18" pageNumber="25" unit="in" value="13.0" valueMax="18.0" valueMin="8.0">8–18 in</quantity>
<quantity box="[435,507,514,537]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="18" pageNumber="25" unit="mm" value="10.0">10 µm</quantity>
. Areolae of variable size and shape, 
<quantity box="[898,992,514,537]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.175" metricValueMax="3.81" metricValueMin="2.54" pageId="18" pageNumber="25" unit="in" value="12.5" valueMax="15.0" valueMin="10.0">10–15 in</quantity>
<quantity box="[999,1071,514,537]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="18" pageNumber="25" unit="mm" value="10.0">10 µm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
